Did you know that 1 in 10 young people experience homelessness at some point in their life? That is why I am proud to be co-chair of this year’s SLEEPOUT for @covenanthousenola! $1 donation challenge is in effect - plus some incentives for those that are able to give more. I have never known what it is like to go without basic necessities like food and shelter. This is why I am so involved with organizations that tackle these issues head on and provide so much joy to our community. Last year I was the top fundraiser because of all of you! Let’s do it again and help make a difference together! Love y’all!!!! #homeless #sleepout #neworleans #nola #community #findyourjoy #gregisms #teamwork
